title: Heiser and Lintker Earn All-MWC Honors; Lady Blues Finish 7th (Illinois College Athletics - Blueboys ...
text: ( Source : Illinois College Athletics - Blueboys and Lady Blues ) Junior Emily Heiser and senior Alexis Lintker ended their seasons with All-Midwest Conference honors by being among the Top 10 finishers at the MWC Championship . ROCKFORD, Ill.
